.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, tea, milk
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, lemon, banana, spinach
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, brazilian, chinese, russian
 1. the person eating spinach is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person eating eggplant is in an odd position##4
 3. the person drinking tea is not the person eating lemon##6
 4. the person drinking milk is the person eating banana##1
 5. the person eating eggplant is the chinese##1
 6. the person eating banana is the russian##1
 7. the person drinking tea is on the right of the brazilian##1
 8. the person eating spinach is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
 9. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person eating spinach and the person drinking tea##7
10. the chinese is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | juice | fanta         | tea    | milk  |
| Food          | spinach     | lemon | eggplant | banana |
| Nationality   | indian     | brazilian     | chinese  | russian |

