.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, rock-climbing, filmmaking, chess
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, italian, polish, thai
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, roller, car
1. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
4. the colombian is between the thai and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not the person driving the car##6
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the italian##7
7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the car##1
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
9. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4      |
| Hobby         | chess | filmmaking  | rock-climbing  | magic-tricks |
| Nationality   | italian   | polish | colombian | thai     |
| Transport     | car    | jet-ski     | quad-bike     | roller         |

