.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, techno, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, chinese, pakistani, brazilian
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, snowmobile, skateboard
1. the fan of techno is on the far right##1
2. the chinese is the person driving the car##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the car##1
4. the fan of d&b is the person driving the car##1
5. the pakistani is the fan of punk##1
6. the colombian is the person driving the boat##1
7. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
8. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere between the fan of d&b and the fan of techno##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | d&b    | classical     | punk   | techno      |
| Nationality   | chinese    | colombian | pakistani | brazilian  |
| Transport     | car | boat  | skateboard    | snowmobile |

