.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, mirinda, coffee
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, dubstep, hip-hop, pop
4 different pets are kept: snake, bird, dog, frog
1. the person drinking 7up is not the fan of pop##6
2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the fan of gospel##7
3. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the fan of dubstep and the person drinking milk##7
5. the person drinking milk is the owner of the frog##1
6. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the dog is the person drinking coffee##1
8. the fan of gospel is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | milk  | 7up | mirinda | coffee |
| Music-Genre   | pop | hip-hop  | dubstep  | gospel    |
| Pet           | frog | snake  | bird    | dog    |

