4. the person drinking water is somewhere between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's hobby is dancing##7
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person drinking coffee##1
6. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking water##1
7. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
8. the person drinking water is not the argentine##6

