The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, adventure, mystery, scientific
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, guinea-pig, dog, ferret
 1. the owner of the dog is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 3. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
 4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is rabbiting is on the far left##1
 6. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
 7. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching scientific movies##7
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 9. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
10. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | rabbiting | chess      | singing | card-games |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery     | adventure | superhero  | scientific       |
| Pet           | ferret         | dog       | rabbit    | guinea-pig  |

