 5. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the spanish##5
 6. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
 7. the nigerian is not the person drinking juice##6
 8. the person driving the van is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
 9. the british is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5
10. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the van##1
11. the british is between the japanese and the nigerian##2

.:: Answer ::.
