.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-14::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, strawberry, artichoke, cauliflower
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, house, rock
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, tennis, soccer, sailing
1. the fan of dubstep is somewhere between the person who's sport is tennis and the fan of rock##7
2. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere between the person who's sport is tennis and the fan of dubstep##7
3. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
4. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5
5. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
6. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
7. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
8. the fan of rock is somewhere to the right of the fan of dubstep##5
9. the person who's sport is soccer is not the fan of ambient##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Food          | potato | cauliflower | artichoke          | strawberry  |
| Music-Genre   | house    | ambient      | dubstep    | rock   |
| Sport         | tennis | cricket  | soccer | sailing |

