5. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5
6. the person eating banana is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
7. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
8. the person watching fantasy movies is not the person who's sport is weightlifting##6
9. the person watching epic movies is the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
